node.text:
.......
After all these years if pretty proud that I still refuse to fake or stage anything on the show. Drama will always come organically if you wait for it.
If we make it, we make it. 
If we fail, we fail. 

Here’s a cell phone video shot of the badass Delorean Hovercraft team making it work with 30 seconds left!
Yea I had to get pissed and ride them hard the whole week. But in the end? They made one of the best builds in the history of the show! 

Congrats guys enjoy those @snapon_official Tools!

You can check out this episode and all the others Now on @discoveryplus 

#jessejames
#monstergarage

So let’s do another SummerKeychain Contest!!

It’s been 8 years since our first keychain contest. I think I want to go back to a design similar to the original. But for sure stainless steel and a different stamp. 
Of course All made by me!

-1st Place: All Expenses paid trip to my personal shop for a week to learn the skills of your choice or A JJFU Cisco 1911.

-2nd Place: A JJFU Nomad 5.56 Rifle or a West Coast Choppers CFL Frame kit.

3rd Place: $1000 spending spree on JesseJames.com

Let me know in the comments if this sounds cool! 

Also Also if you’re one of those mofos that likes a bargin!
You can take the early bird special before we officially launch next week. The price will definitely go up!

PayPal $25 (friends/family)

—> Popeofwelding@jjfu.com 

Make sure you put Full Name and Shipping Address in the notes!

Don’t be shy! The more you buy the more chances you have to win🏆🏆🏆🏆

This is going to be Fun!

#jessejames

“Creativity and ego cannot go together.
If you free yourself from comparing and jealous mind, your creativity opens up endlessly. 
Just as water springs from a fountain, creatively springs from every moment.
You must not be your own obstacle. 
You must not be owned by the environment you are in.
You must own the environment, the phenomenal world around you.
You must be able to freely move in and out of your mind.
This is being free.”

~ Jeong Kwan

( 📸 @jason.elias )

node.text:
Welcome to the New Era!

We are very happy to announce that our New Pro Fab Person-Welder is in fact, a WOMAN!!

Please meet Briana Huhn ( @huhney_bee ) who has joined the West Coast Choppers, JJFU, Texas Hot Rods team.
I was lucky enough to work side by side with Briana on the new season of Monster Garage. Her and I tag team welded a 18’ long stainless steel jet engine. I was very impressed with her work ethic and skill set. She completely supersedes any kind of male/female pronoun designation. She is just a plain all around badass fabricator in any gender. She’s not afraid to jump in and get dirty and handle things.
This week was her first full week at the shop. So we broke in with Texas style BBQ for our shop lunch.

Please comment and give her a shout out and make feel at home in the Texas Hill Country

👉🏽👉🏽 @huhney_bee 👈🏽👈🏽

Thanks

#jessejames
@popeofwelding
